item.title: Ep 133. Securing Supply Chains in C++, Java and Javascript
item.description: In episode 133 of The Secure Developer, we delve into the subject of supply chain security across various ecosystems and languages, guided by industry experts Liran Tal and Roy Ram from Snyk. Liran is the Director of Developer Advocacy at Snyk and has a background working particularly in Node.js and JavaScript. Roy is a Senior Product Manager serving as part of the product team for Snyk Code, and has a background in cybersecurity and a solid understanding of C++... Feed: https://feeds.simplecast.com/47yfLpm0
